<br>
AA abilities<br>
-----------<br>
Mental Reclusion - 5 levels (2/4/6/8/10 30pts)<br>
  Passive<br>
  PreReq: Mental Clarity 3<br>
  This ability allows you to raise your Flowing Thought Cap by 1 per level.<br>
<br>
Mental Certainty -  3 Levels (3/6/9 18pts)<br>
  Passive<br>
  PreReq: SCM 3, MC 3<br>
  A hybrid of SCM and MC that stacks with both. Each level adds roughly half of previous versions to each. <br>
<br>
Mana Surge (5pts)<br>
  Active<br>
  PreReq: Mental Clarity 3<br>
  This ability gives a chance to add 1-20% damage to every spell at a 10% loss of mana efficiency.  Useable once every 2 hrs, Lasts for 60 seconds. Stacks with Manaburn.<br>
 *Your Hands crackle with Magic Force*<br>
 *Your hands return to normal*<br>
<br>
Mana Burst (5pts)<br>
  Active<br>
  PreReq: Mental Clarity 3<br>
  This ability is treated exactly as Mana Burn with the exception that all mobs in a point blank radius take half damage. <br>
<br>
Mastery of Destruction (2/4/6/8/10 30pts)<br>
  Passive<br>
  PreReq: SCFM 3, Level 61-65 respectively<br>
  This ability effectively raises your crit cap by .2 per level.<br>
  i.e. 2.2 for level 1, 2.8 for level 4<br>
<br>
Fury of Ro (5pts)<br>
  Active<br>
  PreReq: SCFM3<br>
  This ability can only be used once very 30 mins. It lasts 30 seconds. All Fire spells critical during this period.<br>
 *Your Body Burns with Power*<br>
 *Your Body Begins to Cool*<br>
<br>
Fury of E'ci (5pts)<br>
  PreReq: SCFM3<br>
  This ability can only be used once very 30 mins. It lasts 30 seconds. All Ice spells critical during this period.<br>
 *Your Blood Freezes Solid!*<br>
 *Your Blood Once More Flows!*<br>
 <br>
Dragon Blooded (9pts)<br>
  Passive<br>
  PreReq: Advanced Innate Fire and Cold Resists 5, Spell Casting Mastery 3<br>
  Fire and Cold Resist +30, +2 Health Regen, +1 Flowing Thought Cap<br>
<br>
True Sorcery (9pts)<br>
  Passive<br>
  PreReq: Advanced Innate Magic Resist 5, Spell Casting Expertise 3, Mastery of the Past 3<br>
  Magic Resist +30, +2 Mana Regen, +300 Mana Pool.<br>
<br>
Chain Casting (3 Levels)<br>
  Passive<br>
  PreReq: SCF 3<br>
  Lowers the recast timer by 2, 5, 9 seconds. This has no effect on spells with instant recast time.<br>
<br>
Mark of Chaos (9pts)<br>
 Active/Deactive<br>
 PreReq: All Spell Casting Fury Lines<br>
 You summon energies with Recklace Abandon. All Mana Costs Flux from -20% to +20%. All Final Damage totals Flux from -20% to +20%. You gain a +3% chance to critical.  You have a 1% backfire chance .(You take 1/2 damage from your spell and only deliver half damage to your target)<br>
<br>
<br>
    <br>
<br>
Spells<br>
-------<br>
<br>
Banish Lv 59<br>
  Single Target Translocate Enemy back to Spawn Point and wipe Aggro. Only works against undamaged mobs. Good Failure Chance modified by Magic Resistance of target.  HIGH HIGH AGGRO.<br>
<br>
Dimensional Ward Lv 55<br>
-- Self-Only  Anti-Summons Buff. When a mob would summon you, buff is destroyed and you are stunned.<br>
<br>
Dimensional Anchor Lv 55<br>
 -- Prevent a Mob from Gating for max 10 seconds. This ability stacks with other Dimensional spells.<br>
<br>
Dimensional Seal  Lv 61<br>
 -- Prevent a Mob from Gating for max 15 seconds.<br>
<br>
Dimensional Rift  Lv 64<br>
-- Prevent a Mob from Gating for max 20 seconds.<br>
<br>
God's  Bane  Lv 65<br>
  -- 4k damage to Planar Boss Mobs.<br>
<br>
Magic Circle: Plane of Disease, Plane of Fire, Plane of Storms etc..etc.. Lv Variable 61 - 65<br>
 -- Your group is surrounded by a circle of protection.  While on the appropriate plane, this provides a zone &quot;Safe Point&quot; for your group to rest. No group member that stays within the circle will gain aggro unless he attacks a mob. This spell will have no effect on someone that already has aggro. This spell does not function in dungeons. Simply on the plane it was intended for only.<br>
 <br>
Shadow Warp Lv 55<br>
-- Self Only Reverse Call of the Hero. Click on member of party, cast it, arrive where they are.<br>
<br>
 <br>
Disentegrate *Revised* Lv 60<br>
  -- Make this spell useful.  Give it a chance to kill any mob. The higher the level the less the chance. Make it stun the wizard for a good length of time after cast.<br>
<br>
Mass Disentegrate Lv 63<br>
 -- Make this spell effect an area. <br>
<br>
Fly  Lv 62<br>
 -- Extremly long lasting levitation, with speed increase and no batwing needed.<br>
<br>
Finally Ancient Spells<br>
-----------------------<br>
I really like the idea of very rare Uber Spells.  Assuming that 65th level will be the final rise in levels (And I guess only Verant knows). I'd like to see an Ancient Line get setup. These are extremely rare and useful spells.<br>
